ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of CYNTHIA PRICE VERREAULT of Montréal, Quebec, to be Chairperson of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Immigration at Pier 21, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective March 3, 2024, in the place of Robert Vineberg, whose term will expire.
